/span>” </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y59 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls9 ws0">特别伟大的圣天论师，在《四百论》中亦云：<span class="_ _6"></span><span class="ls1a">“如来所</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">说法，<span class="_ _3"></span>略言唯二种：</div><div class="t m0 x1b he y5b ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">槃</div><div class="t m0 x12 h4 y5a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">不害生人天，<span class="_ _3"></span>观空证涅<span class="_ _d"> </span>。<span class="_ _6"></span>”<span class="_ _3"></span>也就是说，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">释迦牟尼佛所宣讲的一切法，<span class="_ _5"></span>概括来说有两种，<span class="_ _5"></span>一种是通达</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">万法皆空的智慧，一种就是不害任何众生的慈悲。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y5e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这种慈悲，<span class="_ _5"></span>不单单是一种口号，<span class="_ _5"></span>而且淋漓尽致地展现在</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">佛教的方方面面。<span class="_ _3"></span>就拿藏传佛教中的<span class="_ _7"></span>“藏医”<span class="_ _3"></span>来说，<span class="_ _7"></span>从古至</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
